1
00:00:08,820 --> 00:00:10,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Boy, I have a favor to ask.</font>

2
00:00:13,300 --> 00:00:14,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wish to work.</font>

3
00:00:14,530 --> 00:00:17,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You want to... work?!</font>

4
00:00:17,490 --> 00:00:21,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I cannot simply remain here 
as a freeloader any longer!</font>

5
00:00:21,570 --> 00:00:23,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What brought this on?</font>

6
00:00:23,120 --> 00:00:24,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure you know</font>

7
00:00:24,560 --> 00:00:28,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that every time Teal visits 
me, she brings me magicite.</font>

8
00:00:29,170 --> 00:00:31,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here you go, guardian deity!</font>

9
00:00:32,510 --> 00:00:36,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just how much of her paycheck 
is she spending on me?</font>

10
00:00:36,410 --> 00:00:38,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you don't want to be a gigolo anymore.</font>

11
00:00:38,760 --> 00:00:40,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please.</font>

12
00:00:42,130 --> 00:00:44,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, it seems like you're 
prepared for this.</font>

13
00:00:44,810 --> 00:00:46,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, then, let's begin...</font>

14
00:00:46,560 --> 00:00:49,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gar's great reformation!</font>

15
00:02:21,460 --> 00:02:25,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am Gar. I wish to 
register as an adventurer.</font>

16
00:02:25,130 --> 00:02:27,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Will this suffice for my paperwork?</font>

17
00:02:27,470 --> 00:02:29,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">U-Um...</font>

18
00:02:29,500 --> 00:02:32,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is a friend of the Magic 
Swordsman of Black Lightning.</font>

19
00:02:32,420 --> 00:02:36,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He may look a bit shady, 
but he can be trusted.</font>

20
00:02:37,290 --> 00:02:40,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kramen! Kramen!</font>

21
00:02:40,980 --> 00:02:43,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it? I'm busy, you know.</font>

22
00:02:43,640 --> 00:02:45,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't bother lying!</font>

23
00:02:45,510 --> 00:02:49,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know you were just admiring the lunch 
your wife packed for you and grinning!</font>

24
00:02:49,270 --> 00:02:51,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! Not so <i>loud</i>!</font>

25
00:02:54,980 --> 00:02:58,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't be bothered to comment on this 
spectacle, so I'll just ask.</font>

26
00:02:58,030 --> 00:02:58,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So what's up?</font>

27
00:02:59,350 --> 00:03:01,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wish to register as an adventurer.</font>

28
00:03:02,670 --> 00:03:03,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

29
00:03:03,640 --> 00:03:05,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's okay?!</font>

30
00:03:05,040 --> 00:03:07,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Magic Swordsman here 
will be responsible for him.</font>

31
00:03:07,430 --> 00:03:09,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Indeed! I guarantee it!</font>

32
00:03:10,180 --> 00:03:12,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There you go. You're registered.</font>

33
00:03:12,750 --> 00:03:13,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thank you.</font>

34
00:03:13,940 --> 00:03:16,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, we will return tomorrow 
to accept a quest.</font>

35
00:03:16,610 --> 00:03:19,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Find us one that you deem 
suitable for a beginner.</font>

36
00:03:19,660 --> 00:03:20,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Farewell!</font>

37
00:03:23,970 --> 00:03:26,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why did we not accept a quest today?</font>

38
00:03:26,280 --> 00:03:28,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You need to prepare a weapon and stuff.</font>

39
00:03:28,020 --> 00:03:29,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can use my magic—</font>

40
00:03:29,700 --> 00:03:30,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh.</font>

41
00:03:30,750 --> 00:03:32,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Exactly.</font>

42
00:03:32,200 --> 00:03:35,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The moment you use dark magic, 
everyone will know you're a demon.</font>

43
00:03:35,140 --> 00:03:36,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You gotta be careful.</font>

44
00:03:36,860 --> 00:03:39,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Also, you don't know anything 
about Minerva, right?</font>

45
00:03:39,600 --> 00:03:41,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll spend today showing you around.</font>

46
00:03:41,810 --> 00:03:43,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I appreciate the trouble.</font>

47
00:03:43,110 --> 00:03:45,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you talking about? You're...</font>

48
00:03:45,890 --> 00:03:49,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">going to be the Magic Swordsman 
of Black Lightning's partner!</font>

49
00:03:49,470 --> 00:03:51,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I would rather not.</font>

50
00:03:53,920 --> 00:03:55,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're here to take a quest!</font>

51
00:03:55,320 --> 00:03:57,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Must you be so loud first 
thing in the morning?</font>

52
00:03:57,290 --> 00:04:00,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, someone's here looking for you.</font>

53
00:04:00,430 --> 00:04:02,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For the Magic Swordsman 
of Black Lightning?</font>

54
00:04:02,750 --> 00:04:03,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Has something happened?</font>

55
00:04:04,330 --> 00:04:06,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's waiting behind the guild.</font>

56
00:04:06,390 --> 00:04:07,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't make her wait too long.</font>

57
00:04:09,830 --> 00:04:11,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've been waiting for you...</font>

58
00:04:12,450 --> 00:04:15,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Magic Swordsman of Black Lightning.</font>

59
00:04:16,010 --> 00:04:17,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cecilia?!</font>

60
00:04:17,400 --> 00:04:19,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So it really is you, Yoki!</font>

61
00:04:19,530 --> 00:04:20,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?!</font>

62
00:04:20,530 --> 00:04:23,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">N-No, this is, um... How do I put it...</font>

63
00:04:23,530 --> 00:04:27,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My name is not Yoki! It is "Magic 
Swordsman of Black Lightning"!</font>

64
00:04:27,530 --> 00:04:29,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yoki.</font>

65
00:04:29,980 --> 00:04:33,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry. I know what 
I'm doing is stupid.</font>

66
00:04:33,540 --> 00:04:34,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You do?</font>

67
00:04:34,940 --> 00:04:36,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But how did you know?</font>

68
00:04:36,790 --> 00:04:39,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sophia told me.</font>

69
00:04:39,960 --> 00:04:43,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She said the Magic Swordsman of 
Black Lightning showed up again.</font>

70
00:04:44,040 --> 00:04:46,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I had heard rumors about him before,</font>

71
00:04:46,730 --> 00:04:50,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font color="#ffffff">but the more I heard, the 
more it sounded like you.</font></font>

72
00:04:51,370 --> 00:04:55,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was worried some kind of uproar 
might ensue, so I came to find out.</font>

73
00:04:55,980 --> 00:04:58,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Kramen leaked my identity, didn't he?</i></font>

74
00:05:00,710 --> 00:05:03,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So that's what's going on!</font>

75
00:05:03,070 --> 00:05:07,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you dressed as the Magic Swordsman 
so that Gar won't be conspicuous?</font>

76
00:05:07,700 --> 00:05:09,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, something like that!</font>

77
00:05:09,530 --> 00:05:12,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">According to my plans, this 
look is the way to go!</font>

78
00:05:12,630 --> 00:05:14,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll help, too.</font>

79
00:05:14,290 --> 00:05:15,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?!</font>

80
00:05:15,080 --> 00:05:17,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd be too worried to let 
you handle this alone.</font>

81
00:05:18,420 --> 00:05:19,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right...</font>

82
00:05:19,610 --> 00:05:22,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, let's start with a 
beginner-friendly quest.</font>

83
00:05:24,620 --> 00:05:27,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We are here from the adventurers' guild 
about the quest to find your pet!</font>

84
00:05:27,610 --> 00:05:29,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tell us your story!</font>

85
00:05:30,190 --> 00:05:34,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey. The clients appear to have frozen.</font>

86
00:05:34,490 --> 00:05:37,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hah! I guess they were 
captivated by my appearance.</font>

87
00:05:37,250 --> 00:05:41,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Magic Swordsman, would you please 
keep your mouth shut for the moment?</font>

88
00:05:42,360 --> 00:05:45,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For starters, please tell us 
how we can identify your cat.</font>

89
00:05:45,680 --> 00:05:49,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can you describe its color, 
size, and tail shape?</font>

90
00:05:51,120 --> 00:05:53,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's taking care to watch and learn.</i></font>

91
00:06:00,860 --> 00:06:03,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the description 
of their missing kitten.</font>

92
00:06:03,780 --> 00:06:07,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's very clever and always came 
back home after going outside,</font>

93
00:06:07,950 --> 00:06:10,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but this time, it's been
missing since last week.</font>

94
00:06:10,740 --> 00:06:12,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How shall we search for it?</font>

95
00:06:12,540 --> 00:06:14,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We should start by asking around.</font>

96
00:06:14,470 --> 00:06:19,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's standard practice to ask the 
neighbors and any patrolling knights.</font>

97
00:06:19,090 --> 00:06:20,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">However...</font>

98
00:06:20,250 --> 00:06:22,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will go above and beyond that!</font>

99
00:06:22,480 --> 00:06:23,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hup!</font>

100
00:06:25,690 --> 00:06:29,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My enhanced sense of smell picked 
up the cat's scent from its owners!</i></font>

101
00:06:29,860 --> 00:06:32,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And now I'll use Instant 
Lightning to run faster</i></font>

102
00:06:32,480 --> 00:06:35,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and run all over town 
looking for that cat!</i></font>

103
00:06:41,050 --> 00:06:42,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I found you.</font>

104
00:06:44,020 --> 00:06:49,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hah! You've instinctively sensed 
my strength and put up your guard?</font>

105
00:06:49,000 --> 00:06:52,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Relax. The Magic Swordsman of 
Black Lightning is your friend.</font>

106
00:06:54,510 --> 00:06:57,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see I have no choice 
but to put you to sleep.</font>

107
00:06:57,060 --> 00:06:58,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Holy Bell.</font>

108
00:07:07,320 --> 00:07:09,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you so much!</font>

109
00:07:09,610 --> 00:07:11,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But... where'd this cat come from?</font>

110
00:07:11,470 --> 00:07:13,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was with your cat.</font>

111
00:07:13,250 --> 00:07:17,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've healed its wounds, so please 
look after it as well, if you can.</font>

112
00:07:17,450 --> 00:07:19,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, farewell!</font>

113
00:07:20,230 --> 00:07:22,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So our quest is complete now?</font>

114
00:07:22,170 --> 00:07:22,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

115
00:07:23,370 --> 00:07:26,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now we just need to inform the 
guild that we've finished it,</font>

116
00:07:26,760 --> 00:07:28,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and we'll receive our reward money.</font>

117
00:07:28,590 --> 00:07:29,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

118
00:07:29,840 --> 00:07:32,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right! On to the next quest!</font>

119
00:07:32,110 --> 00:07:33,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait a minute!</font>

120
00:07:33,180 --> 00:07:36,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No one can do things the way 
you do, Magic Swordsman.</font>

121
00:07:36,640 --> 00:07:39,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This won't give Gar any experience.</font>

122
00:07:40,760 --> 00:07:41,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry.</font>

123
00:07:41,640 --> 00:07:43,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This time, we'll put Gar up front</font>

124
00:07:43,910 --> 00:07:46,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and have him do as much 
as he can on his own.</font>

125
00:07:46,490 --> 00:07:50,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-All right. But I will still 
depend on you to show me the way.</font>

126
00:07:50,030 --> 00:07:51,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know the land.</font>

127
00:07:51,290 --> 00:07:53,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have nothing to worry about!</font>

128
00:07:53,450 --> 00:07:58,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have me, the Magic Swordsman 
of Black Lightning, behind you!</font>

129
00:08:00,970 --> 00:08:02,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This must be the herb.</font>

130
00:08:02,500 --> 00:08:03,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Listen up, Gar.</font>

131
00:08:04,060 --> 00:08:07,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gathering herbs is a path all 
adventurers must walk at some point.</font>

132
00:08:07,410 --> 00:08:09,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't take any more than you need,</font>

133
00:08:09,270 --> 00:08:11,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">or there won't be enough left for others.</font>

134
00:08:11,430 --> 00:08:13,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, I understand.</font>

135
00:08:14,040 --> 00:08:15,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Will this suffice?</font>

136
00:08:15,840 --> 00:08:17,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, looks good.</font>

137
00:08:17,700 --> 00:08:21,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now you, too, have taken a step 
toward even greater heigh—</font>

138
00:08:20,270 --> 00:08:22,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Good. Let's move on to the next quest.</font>

139
00:08:23,770 --> 00:08:26,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The next quest is taking out some goblins.</font>

140
00:08:26,700 --> 00:08:30,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This will probably be Gar's first battle.</font>

141
00:08:30,010 --> 00:08:31,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll have to support him...</font>

142
00:08:35,580 --> 00:08:37,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't think there'll 
be any need for that.</font>

143
00:08:37,920 --> 00:08:39,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's all thanks to the power of love!</font>

144
00:08:39,810 --> 00:08:42,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, the power of 
escaping the gigolo life!</font>

145
00:08:42,180 --> 00:08:43,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not a gigolo!</font>

146
00:08:44,770 --> 00:08:47,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yep, you've completed 
the quest, all right.</font>

147
00:08:47,780 --> 00:08:49,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here's your reward.</font>

148
00:08:53,830 --> 00:08:56,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So this is what it means to work.</font>

149
00:08:57,470 --> 00:08:59,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Teal has been working all this time</font>

150
00:08:59,830 --> 00:09:03,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font color="#ffffff">and making money, despite 
her weak constitution...</font></font>

151
00:09:03,640 --> 00:09:05,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will work even more!</font>

152
00:09:05,870 --> 00:09:08,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I will repay the debt I owe Teal!</font>

153
00:09:08,900 --> 00:09:09,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's the spirit!</font>

154
00:09:09,940 --> 00:09:11,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're rooting for you, Gar!</font>

155
00:09:11,810 --> 00:09:14,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll back you up with all 
we've got tomorrow, too!</font>

156
00:09:14,340 --> 00:09:17,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry, but could you allow 
me to do this myself from now on?</font>

157
00:09:17,960 --> 00:09:18,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

158
00:09:18,500 --> 00:09:19,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it's too soon for you to...</font>

159
00:09:19,970 --> 00:09:23,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry. I won't cause any problems.</font>

160
00:09:23,110 --> 00:09:26,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have a good idea of how 
to carry out quests now.</font>

161
00:09:28,170 --> 00:09:30,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'd better come back strong enough</font>

162
00:09:30,380 --> 00:09:34,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to be the Magic Swordsman of 
Black Lightning's right-hand man!</font>

163
00:09:34,940 --> 00:09:37,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll be looking forward to your return!</font>

164
00:09:38,770 --> 00:09:40,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyway, the sun's going down.</font>

165
00:09:40,840 --> 00:09:42,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Time to part ways for now.</font>

166
00:09:42,390 --> 00:09:44,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you have plans after this?</font>

167
00:09:44,600 --> 00:09:47,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Since I'm the Magic Swordsman 
of Black Lightning now,</font>

168
00:09:47,590 --> 00:09:49,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going on a Rank A quest.</font>

169
00:09:51,710 --> 00:09:52,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll go with you.</font>

170
00:09:52,840 --> 00:09:53,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wut?!</font>

171
00:09:53,910 --> 00:09:59,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But, um... most Rank A quests 
require a few days' travel time.</font>

172
00:09:59,370 --> 00:10:01,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you're, well... busy, aren't you?</font>

173
00:10:02,370 --> 00:10:04,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not a problem right now!</font>

174
00:10:04,200 --> 00:10:07,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or... would I be a burden?</font>

175
00:10:07,460 --> 00:10:08,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course I'd be happy to have you!</font>

176
00:10:09,460 --> 00:10:12,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But this won't be so much 
a quest as a journey!</i></font>

177
00:10:13,000 --> 00:10:15,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Before now, we've had tea together</i></font>

178
00:10:15,340 --> 00:10:17,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and traveled with friends, but...</i></font>

179
00:10:17,300 --> 00:10:18,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>several days of just the two of us?!</i></font>

180
00:10:18,970 --> 00:10:22,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">B-But you'd be uncomfortable 
camping out in those clothes.</font>

181
00:10:22,990 --> 00:10:25,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you don't have gear 
for long journeys, do you?</font>

182
00:10:25,130 --> 00:10:26,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Very well.</font>

183
00:10:26,470 --> 00:10:28,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then please wait here for a little while.</font>

184
00:10:28,730 --> 00:10:29,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

185
00:10:36,310 --> 00:10:37,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry I kept you waiting!</font>

186
00:10:43,750 --> 00:10:45,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cecily the adventurer at your service!</font>

187
00:10:46,120 --> 00:10:47,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cecily?</font>

188
00:10:47,080 --> 00:10:49,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm all set for a long journey now,</font>

189
00:10:49,460 --> 00:10:53,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and in this outfit, no one will know 
I'm Cecilia from the hero's party.</font>

190
00:10:53,660 --> 00:10:55,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So now there's no problem, right?</font>

191
00:10:59,560 --> 00:11:02,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kramen sure was happy, wasn't he?</font>

192
00:11:02,430 --> 00:11:05,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He said we were taking care of a 
real pain-in-the-ass quest for him,</font>

193
00:11:05,780 --> 00:11:07,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but we're just inspecting some ruins.</font>

194
00:11:07,560 --> 00:11:09,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How hard can that be?</font>

195
00:11:09,060 --> 00:11:13,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rank A quests aren't just about 
fighting strong monsters.</font>

196
00:11:13,670 --> 00:11:17,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Also, there are no villages we can 
rest in on the way to these ruins.</font>

197
00:11:17,980 --> 00:11:20,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, and no real road, 
either. Kinda inconvenient.</font>

198
00:11:20,820 --> 00:11:24,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Verifying our route to the 
ruins will be dangerous.</font>

199
00:11:24,410 --> 00:11:27,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">On top of that, we have to search 
inside without ransacking them.</font>

200
00:11:28,170 --> 00:11:31,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Assume we won't be able to use 
attack magic as a general rule.</font>

201
00:11:31,750 --> 00:11:33,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But what if monsters show up?</font>

202
00:11:33,740 --> 00:11:35,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We do everything we can to avoid combat.</font>

203
00:11:35,930 --> 00:11:39,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Studying the monsters that live 
in the ruins is part of the quest.</font>

204
00:11:39,000 --> 00:11:40,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're sure asking a lot...</font>

205
00:11:40,970 --> 00:11:44,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The client is an archaeologist 
from a research institution.</font>

206
00:11:44,620 --> 00:11:47,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This quest is probably very 
important to the guild.</font>

207
00:11:47,500 --> 00:11:50,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They must really trust 
you, Magic Swordsman.</font>

208
00:11:50,310 --> 00:11:52,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I'll have to give it my all, then.</font>

209
00:11:54,330 --> 00:11:56,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shall we start preparing to make camp?</font>

210
00:12:07,250 --> 00:12:08,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We're camping out together!</i></font>

211
00:12:08,680 --> 00:12:11,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We're spending the night alone together!</i></font>

212
00:12:11,480 --> 00:12:15,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Any other time, I'd probably 
panic and get all nervous,</i></font>

213
00:12:15,790 --> 00:12:17,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but now, it's no problem!</i></font>

214
00:12:17,690 --> 00:12:18,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Because...</i></font>

215
00:12:18,890 --> 00:12:22,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can play it all off by 
going into chuuni mode!</i></font>

216
00:12:23,690 --> 00:12:25,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am the Magic Swordsman 
of Black Lightning.</font>

217
00:12:25,720 --> 00:12:28,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will make even camping out 
a comfortable experience!</font>

218
00:12:31,480 --> 00:12:33,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've assured that our 
surroundings are safe.</font>

219
00:12:33,960 --> 00:12:34,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And...</font>

220
00:12:34,730 --> 00:12:38,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've gathered fruits and vegetables 
for our rations, as well!</font>

221
00:12:38,230 --> 00:12:40,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You certainly are efficient.</font>

222
00:12:41,190 --> 00:12:44,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No one else is around. Why 
don't you take the mask off?</font>

223
00:12:44,740 --> 00:12:46,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That I cannot do!</font>

224
00:12:46,440 --> 00:12:49,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Until this quest is over, I am the 
Magic Swordsman of Black Lightning!</font>

225
00:12:49,700 --> 00:12:51,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To show my true identity 
would be inexcusable!</font>

226
00:12:51,550 --> 00:12:52,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Incidentally...</font>

227
00:12:54,500 --> 00:12:57,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've made it so I can 
still eat with it on!</font>

228
00:12:58,000 --> 00:12:59,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's bad manners!</font>

229
00:13:00,750 --> 00:13:02,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry! I'll take it off!</font>

230
00:13:07,850 --> 00:13:10,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, then, I'll dish up the soup.</font>

231
00:13:20,130 --> 00:13:22,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here you go. It's very simple, but...</font>

232
00:13:22,900 --> 00:13:24,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks.</font>

233
00:13:28,360 --> 00:13:29,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's good!</font>

234
00:13:29,610 --> 00:13:32,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, there's no way anything 
you cook wouldn't be good!</font>

235
00:13:33,550 --> 00:13:34,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're exaggerating.</font>

236
00:13:37,170 --> 00:13:39,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-It's the truth!</font>

237
00:13:42,370 --> 00:13:44,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks for dinner! Mask on!</font>

238
00:13:45,700 --> 00:13:47,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Be still, my soul!</font>

239
00:13:47,460 --> 00:13:49,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You seem quite flustered to me!</font>

240
00:13:49,180 --> 00:13:51,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">R-Really? Well... that won't do!</font>

241
00:13:51,980 --> 00:13:53,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We should sleep for 
our early start tomorrow!</font>

242
00:13:54,600 --> 00:13:56,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You want to go to sleep already?</font>

243
00:13:56,420 --> 00:13:58,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She's so cute!</i></font>

244
00:13:58,420 --> 00:14:02,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But... somehow, she seems 
different from usual today.</i></font>

245
00:14:02,690 --> 00:14:04,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But Cecilia, you—</font>

246
00:14:04,050 --> 00:14:05,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's Cecily!</font>

247
00:14:05,460 --> 00:14:10,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry. You've been questing since this 
morning, Cecily. You must be tired.</font>

248
00:14:11,380 --> 00:14:13,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just who do you think I am?</font>

249
00:14:14,190 --> 00:14:16,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have completed more quests 
than you, Magic Swordsman.</font>

250
00:14:16,940 --> 00:14:18,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am one of those chosen 
to slay the Demon King</font>

251
00:14:18,930 --> 00:14:20,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">as a member of the hero's party!</font>

252
00:14:21,460 --> 00:14:24,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was just trying to imitate you.</font>

253
00:14:24,640 --> 00:14:26,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That freaked me out...</font>

254
00:14:35,490 --> 00:14:39,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry to go against your 
wishes, but I must refuse.</font>

255
00:14:39,980 --> 00:14:42,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am still inexperienced.</font>

256
00:14:42,500 --> 00:14:45,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have no intention of marrying anyone.</font>

257
00:14:45,730 --> 00:14:49,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What, so that funny guy dumped you, then?</font>

258
00:14:49,860 --> 00:14:52,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He has nothing to do with this!</font>

259
00:14:52,120 --> 00:14:53,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh-huh.</font>

260
00:14:53,740 --> 00:14:56,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But this is not a man you can 
turn down for a reason like that.</font>

261
00:14:57,240 --> 00:14:59,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The heir to an influential 
neighboring domain lord</font>

262
00:14:59,690 --> 00:15:02,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">has requested your hand in marriage.</font>

263
00:15:11,760 --> 00:15:13,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, let us away, Cecily!</font>

264
00:15:13,770 --> 00:15:16,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">An adventure yet unseen awaits us!</font>

265
00:15:16,250 --> 00:15:19,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You mustn't yell so 
loudly, Magic Swordsman.</font>

266
00:15:19,080 --> 00:15:21,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If there are monsters nearby, 
you'll provoke them.</font>

267
00:15:21,330 --> 00:15:22,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry.</font>

268
00:15:28,530 --> 00:15:31,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll take the front line today.</font>

269
00:15:31,250 --> 00:15:33,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Shouldn't it be the other way around?</font>

270
00:15:33,280 --> 00:15:37,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your magic is powerful. 
It could damage the ruins.</font>

271
00:15:37,600 --> 00:15:41,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can restrain monsters with 
Saint Chains if necessary.</font>

272
00:15:41,540 --> 00:15:43,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, let me handle this.</font>

273
00:15:43,850 --> 00:15:46,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can tell where monsters are.</font>

274
00:15:46,430 --> 00:15:49,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Plus, I still have plenty of 
magic I haven't shown you yet.</font>

275
00:15:59,800 --> 00:16:01,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There are monsters up ahead.</font>

276
00:16:01,670 --> 00:16:03,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Around thirteen of them.</font>

277
00:16:03,470 --> 00:16:04,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

278
00:16:11,490 --> 00:16:14,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Incredible! You even got the number right!</font>

279
00:16:14,260 --> 00:16:17,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But there are too many 
for me to restrain them.</font>

280
00:16:17,640 --> 00:16:20,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to avoid combat whenever 
possible, so let's go around.</font>

281
00:16:21,250 --> 00:16:24,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No. Leave this to me.</font>

282
00:16:25,290 --> 00:16:26,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Illusion Sphere.</font>

283
00:16:34,680 --> 00:16:36,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't see anything...</font>

284
00:16:36,870 --> 00:16:39,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're going to keep moving. 
Keep your eyes shut.</font>

285
00:16:46,030 --> 00:16:49,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So... what kind of spell did you use?</font>

286
00:16:49,560 --> 00:16:53,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">An intermediate dark spell 
called Illusion Sphere.</font>

287
00:16:53,020 --> 00:16:54,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It shows targets an illusion.</font>

288
00:16:54,970 --> 00:16:58,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When they look at it, they see the 
one thing they find most attractive</font>

289
00:16:58,810 --> 00:17:00,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and can't tear their eyes away.</font>

290
00:17:00,410 --> 00:17:01,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Attractive?</font>

291
00:17:01,710 --> 00:17:03,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The thing they like most, basically.</font>

292
00:17:04,110 --> 00:17:05,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>In my case...</i></font>

293
00:17:05,750 --> 00:17:08,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'd see Cecilia. No doubt.</i></font>

294
00:17:08,840 --> 00:17:10,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And Raven would see Happiness.</i></font>

295
00:17:10,750 --> 00:17:13,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder what I'd see if I looked at it.</font>

296
00:17:13,260 --> 00:17:16,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well... it'd be whatever 
you like the most...</font>

297
00:17:17,800 --> 00:17:19,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In that case...</font>

298
00:17:23,270 --> 00:17:25,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess it'd be cake!</font>

299
00:17:25,020 --> 00:17:26,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's</i> where you went?!</font>

300
00:17:26,410 --> 00:17:27,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, uh... n-nothing!</font>

301
00:17:28,200 --> 00:17:30,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's a convenient spell.</font>

302
00:17:30,070 --> 00:17:32,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's amazing how many different 
types of spells you have.</font>

303
00:17:34,330 --> 00:17:36,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not all there is to my magic!</font>

304
00:17:36,490 --> 00:17:38,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just follow me, and you 
needn't worry about a thing!</font>

305
00:17:51,840 --> 00:17:54,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It looks like this is where the ruins end.</font>

306
00:17:55,180 --> 00:17:59,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cecily... is it normal for ruins 
to be so full of nothing?!</font>

307
00:17:59,430 --> 00:18:01,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, there is an unusual mushroom.</font>

308
00:18:02,680 --> 00:18:03,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No matter how far we go,</font>

309
00:18:03,920 --> 00:18:06,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it's just monsters, plants, 
monsters, plants, and mushrooms!</font>

310
00:18:06,690 --> 00:18:08,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's gotta be more to it than this!</font>

311
00:18:08,650 --> 00:18:10,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like an android 
dormant for millennia,</font>

312
00:18:10,650 --> 00:18:13,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">a sealed magic sword, relics, treasures...</font>

313
00:18:13,590 --> 00:18:15,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll even take the most 
clichéd boss monster!</font>

314
00:18:15,460 --> 00:18:17,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just give me <i>something</i>!</font>

315
00:18:17,110 --> 00:18:18,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not so loud!</font>

316
00:18:18,970 --> 00:18:20,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">R-Right...</font>

317
00:18:20,620 --> 00:18:23,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right, let's head outside.</font>

318
00:18:33,850 --> 00:18:35,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is amazing.</font>

319
00:18:37,590 --> 00:18:38,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

320
00:18:38,670 --> 00:18:40,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess that's the end of that quest.</font>

321
00:18:40,580 --> 00:18:44,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It'll be nighttime soon. Let's 
camp where we did last night.</font>

322
00:18:44,060 --> 00:18:45,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">R-Right...</font>

323
00:18:45,590 --> 00:18:47,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Just the two of us again...</i></font>

324
00:18:47,310 --> 00:18:50,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i><font color="#000000">I </font></i>definitely<i> can't take off the mask now!</i></font>

325
00:18:54,350 --> 00:18:56,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The quest is complete!</font>

326
00:18:56,380 --> 00:18:58,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For the Magic Swordsman of Black Lightning</font>

327
00:18:58,220 --> 00:19:02,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and Cecily, the Guide of Love 
and Mercy, it was no prob—</font>

328
00:19:02,540 --> 00:19:03,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ow!</font>

329
00:19:03,110 --> 00:19:05,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't need a nickname.</font>

330
00:19:05,200 --> 00:19:06,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it's so cool...</font>

331
00:19:06,980 --> 00:19:08,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And? Anything to report?</font>

332
00:19:10,120 --> 00:19:10,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here you are.</font>

333
00:19:11,490 --> 00:19:13,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A... written report?</font>

334
00:19:13,830 --> 00:19:16,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow, this is fantastic!</font>

335
00:19:16,190 --> 00:19:18,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't a verbal report enough?</font>

336
00:19:18,670 --> 00:19:21,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That kind of laziness is exactly why</font>

337
00:19:21,080 --> 00:19:23,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't give a quest like 
this to just anyone.</font>

338
00:19:23,790 --> 00:19:27,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's milady—I mean, Cecily for you!</font>

339
00:19:27,040 --> 00:19:30,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can submit this as is, 
so it's a huge help!</font>

340
00:19:30,940 --> 00:19:32,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here's your reward.</font>

341
00:19:32,190 --> 00:19:35,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's Rank A for you. The reward's huge.</font>

342
00:19:35,170 --> 00:19:37,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's use it to throw a big after-party!</font>

343
00:19:37,510 --> 00:19:40,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That sounds great! But first...</font>

344
00:19:42,160 --> 00:19:44,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you should change clothes.</font>

345
00:19:44,110 --> 00:19:44,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

346
00:19:47,160 --> 00:19:49,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hm? It's unlocked?</font>

347
00:19:58,500 --> 00:20:02,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where is the guardian deity?</font>

348
00:20:04,510 --> 00:20:08,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've been coming here every 
day for the past four days,</font>

349
00:20:08,100 --> 00:20:10,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and he isn't here.</font>

350
00:20:10,410 --> 00:20:14,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I beg of you... if you know 
where he is, please tell me.</font>

351
00:20:14,790 --> 00:20:17,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where has the guardian deity gone?</font>

352
00:20:17,940 --> 00:20:19,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah, boy, you've returned.</font>

353
00:20:19,930 --> 00:20:20,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gar!</font>

354
00:20:20,860 --> 00:20:24,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That voice... The guardian deity?</font>

355
00:20:25,050 --> 00:20:26,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. It's me.</font>

356
00:20:29,160 --> 00:20:33,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Guardian deity!</font>

357
00:20:36,040 --> 00:20:39,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You were away for so long! 
I was worried about you!</font>

358
00:20:39,820 --> 00:20:42,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry I didn't inform you.</font>

359
00:20:42,030 --> 00:20:44,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The truth is, I've rented 
a room near here.</font>

360
00:20:46,050 --> 00:20:48,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've become an adventurer.</font>

361
00:20:48,580 --> 00:20:50,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can make my own living now.</font>

362
00:20:50,810 --> 00:20:54,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you no longer need to overtax 
yourself to buy me magicite.</font>

363
00:20:53,970 --> 00:20:55,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not overtaxing myself!</font>

364
00:20:55,750 --> 00:21:00,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Serving you is my greatest 
happiness in life!</font>

365
00:21:00,170 --> 00:21:02,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please let me continue to serve you!</font>

366
00:21:03,380 --> 00:21:04,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Very well.</font>

367
00:21:06,320 --> 00:21:08,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you!</font>

368
00:21:08,070 --> 00:21:11,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I will still repay my debt to you.</font>

369
00:21:11,170 --> 00:21:15,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But there's no need! As long 
as I'm by your side, I'm happy!</font>

370
00:21:15,450 --> 00:21:18,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um... we're still here, you know...</font>

371
00:21:21,730 --> 00:21:25,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Teal didn't say a word about 
the Magic Swordsman and Cecily.</font>

372
00:21:25,910 --> 00:21:27,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She only had eyes for Gar.</font>

373
00:21:28,630 --> 00:21:31,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Man, for some reason, I'm exhausted.</font>

374
00:21:38,550 --> 00:21:39,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yoki?!</font>

375
00:21:39,590 --> 00:21:40,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I'm done for!</font>

376
00:21:40,780 --> 00:21:44,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Four days' worth of embarrassment 
just hits too hard!</font>

377
00:21:44,780 --> 00:21:46,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sealing this away!</font>

378
00:21:46,740 --> 00:21:47,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, please!</font>

379
00:21:49,270 --> 00:21:52,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's true that the Magic 
Swordsman is out of control,</font>

380
00:21:52,460 --> 00:21:54,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">he draws a lot of negative attention,</font>

381
00:21:54,670 --> 00:21:56,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and he causes trouble 
more often than not...</font>

382
00:21:57,230 --> 00:22:01,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But we came through this quest 
in one piece thanks to his magic.</font>

383
00:22:03,300 --> 00:22:07,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cecily the adventurer would be 
happy to team up with him again.</font>

384
00:22:10,630 --> 00:22:15,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, Adventurer Cecily, there's 
still much more to my magic!</font>

385
00:22:15,670 --> 00:22:17,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you've taken an interest,</font>

386
00:22:17,310 --> 00:22:21,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will show you even greater 
power on our next quest!</font>

387
00:22:22,350 --> 00:22:24,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I look forward to it!</font>

